* 1645年（[[順治|順治]]二年）江寧織造設立。<ref name="南都">{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/sd/2009-02-15/131917218956.shtml |title=江宁织造府复建背后：官商学历经25年利益博弈 |access-date=2010-12-29 |archive-date=2021-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221022416/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/sd/2009-02-15/131917218956.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
